{
  "stem": "9503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well he was what was called an electrical engineer, and he got a job in that Department of the camp that fixed anything that had to do with electricity.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I learned that he even was requested-- he was good-- to do this in the commandant's house, that the commandant asked for him when there was something wrong.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got the job through [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whom-- my mother knew somebody who got him this job to begin with.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do remember that it took a certain amount of purchasing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Westerbork, we were allowed to get packages.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know who sent them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This might have been, you know, employees of my father, but we did get some food packages in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And most of the content of this, my father took to his boss in order to stay in his good graces-- you know, that was money.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was also my father's job that part of the time kept us-- most of the time, kept us in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Not being placed on transport in Westerbork meant what you know, and who you knew, and where you were at the time of a transport.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Transports left every Tuesday morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Every Monday night they would come into the barracks, and there was this terrible silence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would read off the names of those who had to be on transport.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, pandemonium broke out, and this was like every Monday for weeks and weeks, I remember this happening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father immediately had a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother worked in the laundry, and she also, on her day off, cleaned the house or the rooms of this couple who had lived there since the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
